
/* Bare theme name, not an absolute /nix/store path: rofi resolves it from its
   own themes directory at runtime. The previous value pinned the store path of
   rofi-1.7.9+wayland1, which stops existing as soon as the package changes (it
   did, when rofi-wayland was merged into rofi) and is then garbage collected. */
@theme "gruvbox-dark-soft"
